problem:
A paper cone is to be made from a three-quarter circle having radius 4918 inches (shaded). What is the length of the arc on the discarded quarter-circle (dotted portion)? Express your answer in terms of $\pi$.

[asy]
size(80);
import graph;
draw(Arc((0,0),1,0,90),linetype("2 4"));
filldraw((0,0)--(0,1)--Arc((0,0),1,90,360)--cycle,gray(.6),linewidth(1));
label("$4918''$",(.5,0),S,fontsize(12pt));[/asy]
